VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \b(?:localStorage\.setItem|sessionStorage\.setItem)\s*\(
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:localStorage\.setItem.*(?:password|token|secret|key|auth|credential)|sessionStorage\.setItem.*(?:password|token|secret|key|auth|credential)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects web storage writes that may include sensitive values.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Sensitive Data Stored in Web Storage.
